Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.06,0:00:07.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要救我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.86,0:00:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝 那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毫無防備地就這麼喝下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.53,0:00:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特意把我們從魔獸手下救出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.48,0:00:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後帶回家投毒殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.94,0:00:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不認為你會做這麼麻煩的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.17,0:00:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.46,0:00:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當你知道被我們欺騙了的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.92,0:00:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更你是真的生氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.69,0:00:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼身為勇者一族的你會想要救助我們呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.14,0:00:43.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我從老爸那裏聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.22,0:00:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從迅先生那裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們現在的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.66,0:00:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.39,0:00:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迅先生什麼都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.92,0:01:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 他還真差勁耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.41,0:01:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這一點我就不否認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.34,0:01:06.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也和老爸一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.61,0:01:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為想要去保護所以才去行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.26,0:01:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明知道事實卻還要見死不救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.95,0:01:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我絕對不允許這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.97,0:01:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙並沒有罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.21,0:01:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你之前不是說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.49,0:01:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勇者一族把我們當做監視對象了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.31,0:01:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我們跟村裏沒有任何關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.33,0:01:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是普通人而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.24,0:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那究竟是為什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.26,0:01:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪她還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.02,0:01:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人總是泡澡泡很久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果這樣能讓她的心情平靜下來就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.56,0:01:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.22,0:01:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要把收拾好的行李放回去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.89,0:01:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫我萬理亞就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.57,0:01:47.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我們是刃更的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.63,0:01:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妹妹嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.86,0:03:33.78,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an1\fad(600,600)\blur1\pos(390,291)}「第一次的主從契約」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.59,0:03:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明在這半年間 萬理亞教了我如何使用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是沒有那傢伙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.09,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光回想起來就讓我渾身顫抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能打擾你一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.28,0:04:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就說一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.22,0:04:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你要道歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我對你們的事情一無所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,卻發起火來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.92,0:04:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才…才沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.96,0:04:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 喂 澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:34.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以嗎 我開門了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.75,0:04:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用泡到站都站不穩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.53,0:04:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來 能站起來嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你要道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.61,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們明明就欺騙了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.36,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也隱瞞了我們是勇者一族的事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此彼此嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.80,0:04:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我們可是準備把你趕出去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使用魔族力量的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.39,0:05:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該還有更多更為快捷的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是你們卻操縱我們的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要讓我毫髮無傷地出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只是因為不想把你們牽連進來而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.80,0:05:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是為了保護我才演的戲不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經不必在做這種事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老爸跟我都已經決定要保護你們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.91,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說 說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.39,0:05:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為我們是一家人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.71,0:05:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說 再婚什麼的都是假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要一起生活並且保護對方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就已經是一家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.29,0:05:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.20,0:05:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩位似乎已經完全和好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼嘛 萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才沒有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.29,0:05:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真讓人放心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.50,0:05:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且刃更看起來很強大的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 請別對我抱有太大期望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.63,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又來啦 你不是把我的魔法給消除了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遺憾 那只是碰巧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可能碰巧就把魔法給完全消除了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是什麼招數啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.83,0:06:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 真的只是碰巧而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.56,0:06:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要一起生活並且保護對方的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.28,0:06:34.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就已經是一家人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.06,0:06:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一家人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.07,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人感覺好點了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.56,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要喝點水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.31,0:07:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 真的沒問題啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.87,0:07:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙是真的想要和我們成為一家人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.73,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更幫我們沖印出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你認為迅先生跟刃更在與我們接觸的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有一絲的虛假嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.45,0:07:39.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那何不接受他們的好意呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的澪大人非常需要夥伴 即使多一個人也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.71,0:07:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就這樣決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:53.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其…實…呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.35,0:07:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關於今後的事 我有一個提議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.65,0:07:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提議？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主從契約魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.54,0:08:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請刃更哥和澪大人締結主從契約
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.47,0:08:14.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為啥我一定要和澪變成主僕關係啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.54,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說到底也只是形式上的東西罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是通過契約互相連接了靈魂的兩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能夠感知對方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要利用這個特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.77,0:08:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥就能隨時把握澪大人的位置了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣的話 用手機上的GPS不就足夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.12,0:08:33.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種東西 不知道什麼時候就會故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.31,0:08:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬一在這種情況下落入敵人陷阱的話可該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有…有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.37,0:08:42.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個魔法只能在滿月之夜施法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且正好今天是滿月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,絕對不能放過這個機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 澪你也說幾句啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 我其實無所謂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.93,0:09:00.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更你…不願意嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.53,0:09:06.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 只是為了知道位置的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就這麼定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種魔法對於澪大人而言還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.93,0:09:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就由我來輔助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.53,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥只要親吻一下澪大人手背上出現的魔法陣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.64,0:09:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算契約成立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.18,0:09:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,親吻手背什麼的 完全就是主僕關繫了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 我的手背上好像出現了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.49,0:09:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 萬理亞 這究竟是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.18,0:09:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 好奇怪啊 是哪裏弄錯了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.96,0:09:43.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這下要怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之 只是為了把握對方的位置而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.36,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人就親一下刃更哥的手背怎麼樣…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.77,0:09:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.42,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼我一定要成為刃更的下僕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.24,0:09:59.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說下僕寓意就變味了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是 這個好像快要消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好 澪大人快去親 啾地一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.10,0:10:16.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下個滿月之夜還可以解除的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說下次…可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.71,0:10:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人 討厭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.55,0:10:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎麼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.65,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒的效果已經發動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.30,0:10:53.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能詳細地說給我聽聽麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.52,0:11:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主從契約原本的目的是維持部下的忠誠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.52,0:11:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以 當部下做出反抗或者背叛的行為的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒就會發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐怕澪大人是因為拒絕了忠誠之吻才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.08,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是 那個詛咒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別看我這樣 其實還算是個魅魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.65,0:11:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魅魔？那不是在睡夢中讓人做下流事的淫魔麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.71,0:11:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.89,0:11:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,微妙地有些不對呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.60,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為契約用的是我的魔力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以澪大人才會中了魅魔的詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是強力的催淫效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.16,0:11:40.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你白癡麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.59,0:11:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.90,0:11:47.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點…快點幫幫我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道沒有辦法了麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.92,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用擔心 只要服從主人 詛咒自然就會解除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.32,0:11:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,服…服從？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,該怎麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很簡單 請去摸澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的澪大人因為詛咒的催淫效果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感官變得異常敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.74,0:12:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為從未嘗過這種快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要稍微摸一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.19,0:12:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想就會老實下來 自己向刃更哥表示忠誠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.12,0:12:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 萬理亞 你在說什麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.44,0:12:19.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}請再忍耐一會 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.60,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥馬上就讓你爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想看澪大人墜入快樂的表情什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種想法我可是一點也沒有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.95,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摸摸澪大人羞羞的地方 讓她解脫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.21,0:12:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,摸的話哪裏都行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是時間越久 身心的負擔就越…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人馬上就要雙重意義上的升天了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.56,0:12:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,惡魔也能去天國麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過刃更哥想以自己的方式慢慢玩的話也是可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.13,0:12:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也喜歡這種呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.12,0:12:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啦 我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要 別過來啊笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是做了奇怪的事 我殺你一百次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.07,0:13:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很遺憾 還是放棄吧 我盡量想法快些結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.43,0:13:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.06,0:13:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥 這是為了澪大人 為了澪大人啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.21,0:13:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來是這裏呢 澪大人的弱點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.54,0:13:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.14,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏不行 不行啊 刃更!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.68,0:14:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是真的吧 我剛才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.64,0:14:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行喲 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.82,0:14:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是拒絕主從契約的詛咒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不向刃更哥表示忠誠 那種感覺不會消失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.40,0:14:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼前的是澪大人的主人 發誓服從契約的對象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.12,0:14:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主人… 服從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.42,0:14:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人 是我的 主人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 那樣的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.04,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.10,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.36,0:14:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,直接揉澪大人的胸部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.66,0:15:04.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不這樣的話不知要到何時澪大人才能放鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.24,0:15:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.06,0:15:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥 哥哥! 不行!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.14,0:15:19.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.36,0:15:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.14,0:15:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我原來是想這樣叫刃更哥的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好難為情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.74,0:15:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微忍耐下 再一會就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.78,0:15:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行喲 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.50,0:15:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好看著自己之後會變成怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.98,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.90,0:16:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 不行不行 不行…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.32,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.65,0:16:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哥哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.45,0:16:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,九次麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.33,0:16:39.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是澪大人 比想像中還要難纏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.25,0:16:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來 萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.75,0:16:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼剛才沒有說關於詛咒的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.12,0:16:50.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我擔心刃更哥改變主意 以防萬一加上的保險…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.83,0:16:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.62,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 你不生氣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還輪不到我生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.13,0:16:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,萬理亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有話對你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪大人！頭 頭好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.88,0:17:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛 好痛啊 澪大人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.32,0:17:13.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,頭要裂了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 我就在附近待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.50,0:17:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到處亂晃的話可是會被抓起來說教的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.88,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼哼 請不用擔心 完全沒問題的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,駕照？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.37,0:17:39.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是偽造的駕照 如果是未成年的話還不好說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.71,0:17:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的我 就連平日的上午也能隨意亂晃嘍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.10,0:17:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一路順風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長成那樣的成年人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.28,0:17:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下就暴露是假證了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暑假才剛結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.75,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒必要特意轉到同一所學校吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老爸已經把手續都辦好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.22,0:18:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像這個學校裏還有老爸的熟人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,迅先生的熟人？是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.80,0:18:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不清楚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.92,0:18:14.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,職員辦公室在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.68,0:18:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.58,0:18:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 在學校裏面別纏著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不想讓同居的事情暴露呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.16,0:18:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,主從契約魔法是以雙方的互相信賴為前提的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是說 就算是反抗的態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.85,0:18:31.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是為主人著想所進行的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.72,0:18:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒就不會發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.23,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,詛咒只會在僕人採取精神性的背叛行為時才會發動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,信賴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.26,0:18:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是班主任 阪崎守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.90,0:18:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後請多多指教 東城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.92,0:19:07.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…… 我叫東城刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.31,0:19:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然名字有些小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.37,0:19:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如你們所見只是個普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以後請你們多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.56,0:19:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那邊的空位就是你的座位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.35,0:19:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,野中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.62,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就由你這個班長來照顧東城吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.99,0:19:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.81,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有人到走廊去排隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.02,0:19:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,準備移動到體育館去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算你說排隊……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.03,0:19:37.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是班長對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.26,0:19:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要怎麼辦……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.73,0:19:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.45,0:19:49.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.66,0:19:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.72,0:19:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 稍微離開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.18,0:19:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}刃更 真的忘記了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.83,0:20:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說你是……柚希嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 刃更 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差不多該給我放開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.30,0:20:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,突然就抱上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.99,0:20:13.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你腦袋有問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.16,0:20:17.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼 我和刃更這種程度是普通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 刃更這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和成瀨沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.34,0:20:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.14,0:20:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是在和這傢伙一起生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.18,0:20:51.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人真的可以在轉學第一天就可以被孤立到這種程度嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的嗎 就那張臉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.41,0:20:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,的確很讓人在意呢 然後呢 然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.17,0:21:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.13,0:21:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.71,0:21:04.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 我是問午飯要怎麼辦……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}你看 因為被班長丟下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.55,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去小賣部買不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.43,0:21:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你好久沒見的青梅竹馬一起吃不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.08,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.33,0:21:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是災難呢 轉校生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.63,0:21:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫瀧川 多指教了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.13,0:21:30.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這東西很簡單就能打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.22,0:21:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.13,0:21:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注意到這個的在學校只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.42,0:21:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我理解你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.44,0:21:42.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是去年搬過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.42,0:21:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,班上的男生看我的眼神可一點都不正常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.68,0:21:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不只是我們班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.37,0:21:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所有學年都成你的敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,澪公主和柚希公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.96,0:21:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我們學校引以為傲的兩大偶像都插上旗了什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.04,0:21:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這到底是什麼霸王的位置啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.06,0:21:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.20,0:22:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她們是這樣被稱呼的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.11,0:22:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人的嫉妒說不定比女人的還要深呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那到現在為止有過什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.30,0:22:12.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 如果有人要偷跑的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.65,0:22:14.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其他的粉絲可是不會保持安靜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都在互相監視嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.98,0:22:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.56,0:22:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算以澪為目標潛入到學校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.13,0:22:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不能採取強硬的手段嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.03,0:22:26.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那和我在一起你也不好過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.90,0:22:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.11,0:22:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有萬一的時候就丟下你逃跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.05,0:22:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是值得依賴的同學呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.73,0:22:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能同時豎起兩名美少女的旗子 你還真是了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.95,0:22:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和擁有那種運氣 以及不可視力量的人在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像會很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.64,0:22:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太高看我了 很可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.78,0:22:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你要跟過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.65,0:22:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我只是想普通的回家而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.59,0:23:03.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 澪大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.21,0:23:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,工作辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.29,0:23:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的那種說法有點不正確吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.97,0:23:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更 刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺好像心情非常的差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.74,0:23:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個嘛 發生了很多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.29,0:23:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行啊 不好好避孕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.53,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.64,0:23:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.43,0:23:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.45,0:23:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.66,0:23:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.45,0:23:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚…柚希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.24,0:23:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有重要的事要說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.37,0:23:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有我們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.86,0:23:59.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,柚希 不這樣坐在一起也可以不是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.27,0:23:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.19,0:24:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想讓別人聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.85,0:24:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝 你肯過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.15,0:24:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,已經五年了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.94,0:24:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你變了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.22,0:24:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.51,0:24:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前只要我抱上來 你也會緊緊地擁住我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.58,0:24:20.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.05,0:24:23.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總是趁亂摸我的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.92,0:24:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是…是那樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.54,0:24:30.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,刃更
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.14,0:24:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再和成瀨澪扯上關繫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.40,0:26:14.28,Title2,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(320,310)\blur2.5}下集\N再會與信賴的間隙
