Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.83,0:02:38.83,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}暗黒の渦を切り裂く契約者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.88,0:02:49.47,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}「神さえも越え」って叫んだら　探し出して
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.64,0:02:55.77,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}守るべきもの 握りしめた右手で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:03:00.23,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Faraway どんな遠くでも届くよ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:05.99,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}大事なもの無くさない想いなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.99,0:03:12.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Anyway 体で世界から進めるはずさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.99,0:03:16.08,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}未来へ走れ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.48,0:02:23.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}堅信光明 追求希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.49,0:02:28.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}去往明日的道路Never End
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.66,0:02:33.58,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}雙眸中映射著誓言的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.83,0:02:38.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}斬斷這漆黑混沌的契約者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.88,0:02:49.47,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}如果怒吼著「將要超越神明」的話　那就去追尋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.64,0:02:55.77,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}用右手握那緊應要守護的事物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.77,0:03:00.23,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}Faraway 無論多麼遙遠都將握緊你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.23,0:03:05.99,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(100,100)\blur1.5}如果不願失去這份珍貴的思念的話
